    "description": "Get the cheese, then get to the exit. It's that easy! Or is it?<br><br><i>Mouse Dreams</i> is a puzzle platformer with bright, colourful graphics, where you must solve puzzles by pushing boxes, manipulating light, strategically powering objects like moving platforms and doors.<br><br>In this single-screen puzzle platformer, you must navigate increasingly challenging levels with simple platforming and whimsical puzzles. Defy gravity, avoid the ghosts, use moving platforms, and more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239110/extras/488752bad076a1ebe033a49e59f59b5f.poster.avif?t=1683436745\" width=400 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239110/extras/488752bad076a1ebe033a49e59f59b5f.webm?t=1683436745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239110/extras/488752bad076a1ebe033a49e59f59b5f.mp4?t=1683436745\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>Mouse Dreams</i> has been carefully designed to give you a fun, smooth learning curve from the easy early puzzles through to the challenging late-game puzzles. You can always try a different puzzle if you get stuck, then go back and finish those you had trouble with later.",
